title: Bump Topten.RichTextKit from 0.4.137 to 0.4.166
body:
Bumps [Topten.RichTextKit](https://github.com/toptensoftware/richtextkit) from 0.4.137 to 0.4.166.

  • 4da86ac Fixed Incorrect Null Check (#72)
  • 8d1c73d Only break font run manually if no linebreak position is possible (#68)
  • beb262e feat: Add a style parameter to set the style of the inserted text (#70)
